mi_lesion_mass.qsel: SELECT tblConfirmCONFIRM.confirm_idc_str, tblMCP.mass_lv_g, tblMCP.mass_mcp_g, tblMCP.mass_mcp_perc, tblConfirmPerLesion.mi_type, tblConfirmPerLesion.mi_event, Count(tblMCP.id_vessel_study) AS CountOfid_vessel_study, tblConfirmPerLesion.lesion_worst FROM qselFilterMCPMostRecentEntry INNER JOIN ((tblConfirmPerLesion INNER JOIN tblConfirmCONFIRM ON tblConfirmPerLesion.confirm_idc = tblConfirmCONFIRM.[﻿confirm_idc]) INNER JOIN tblMCP ON tblConfirmPerLesion.lesion_id = tblMCP.id_vessel_study) ON qselFilterMCPMostRecentEntry.MaxOfid_datetime_mcp = tblMCP.id_datetime_mcp WHERE (((tblMCP.id_vessel) Like '%dist%') AND ((tblMCP.id_vtree)='sub')) GROUP BY tblConfirmCONFIRM.confirm_idc_str, tblMCP.mass_lv_g, tblMCP.mass_mcp_g, tblMCP.mass_mcp_perc, tblConfirmPerLesion.mi_type, tblConfirmPerLesion.mi_event, tblConfirmPerLesion.lesion_worst HAVING (((tblConfirmPerLesion.mi_event)=1));
